---
import ReasonMiniCard from "./ReasonMiniCard.astro"
---

<article class="parent max-w-lg">
    <div class="div1">
        <h3>Por que escogernos?</h3>
        <p>Somos una empresa que se entrga con dedicacion a la creacion de cosas hermosas</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="div2">
        <ReasonMiniCard></ReasonMiniCard>  
    </div>
    <div class="div3">
        <ReasonMiniCard></ReasonMiniCard>  
    </div>
    <div class="div4">
        <ReasonMiniCard></ReasonMiniCard>  
    </div>
    <div class="div5">
        <ReasonMiniCard></ReasonMiniCard>  
    </div>
</article>

<style>
    .parent {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto, 1fr, 1fr;
    grid-column-gap: 0px;
    grid-row-gap: 0px;
    gap: 20px;
    }

    .div1 { grid-area: 1 / 1 / 2 / 3; }
    .div2 { grid-area: 2 / 1 / 3 / 2; }
    .div3 { grid-area: 2 / 2 / 3 / 3; }
    .div4 { grid-area: 3 / 1 / 4 / 2; }
    .div5 { grid-area: 3 / 2 / 4 / 3; }
</style>